title: Kendall Jenner goes braless under clinging white blouse out to lunch with rapper pal Taco Bennett
text:
She is known for her style on and off the runway.

And Kendall Jenner demonstrated her dress sense again on Tuesday while out to lunch in Los Angeles with her pal Travis 'Taco' Bennett.

The globetrotting 23-year-old supermodel went bra-less beneath a clinging and slightly sheer white top that emphasized her slender frame.

Sleek and chic: Kendall Jenner demonstrated her dress sense again on Tuesday while out to lunch in Los Angeles with her pal Travis 'Taco' Bennett

Letting her luxurious brown hair down, she accentuated her screen siren features with makeup and slid into a pair of grey jeans.

Kendall fired up her Insta Stories while in the car that day to upload selfie footage in which she pulled a pouty smile amid fluttering cartoon butterflies.

This Tuesday Kendall co-starred with her younger sister, 22-year-old cosmetics billionaire Kylie Jenner, in an Instagram ad for their joint fall collection.

Both sisters threw sweaters on over their lingerie, putting their shapely legs on display while sticking to an autumnal theme.

Touch of glitz: Taco wore a simple outfit but added some extra dazzle with a gleaming necklace and a pair of glittering earrings

On the move: Letting her luxurious brown hair down, she accentuated her screen siren features with makeup and slid into a pair of grey jeans

Kendall allegedly out-earns Kylie when it comes to paid Instagram sponsorships, a new Hopper HQ study published on Buzz Bingo claimed.

In the 'Celebrity' category of influencers, Kendall was reported to be at number one at $15.9 million annually with Kylie at number three with $3.8 million.

Their half-sister Khloe Kardashian is number four with $1.2 million, with Selena Gomez number two at $8 million and Priyanka Chopra number five at $1.1 million.

Another year: The daughter of momager extraordinaire Kris Jenner and transgender ex-Olympian Caitlyn Jenner will ring in her 24th birthday this Sunday

The daughter of momager extraordinaire Kris Jenner and transgender ex-Olympian Caitlyn Jenner will ring in her 24th birthday this Sunday.

Kris was famously pregnant with Kendall at the 1994 funeral of her pal Nicole Brown, whose ex-husband O.J. Simpson was controversially acquitted of her murder.

O.J.'s legal team included Kris' own ex-husband Rob Kardashian - the father of her elder four children Kourtney, Kim, Khloe and Rob Kardashian.
